oai_dc:dc.dc:title: French. Lizzie Crozier French (1851-1926).
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Lizzie Crozier French (1851-1926) standing on sidewalk with Park House, Knoxville, TN, in background. Shown later in life, holding a bouquet of flowers. She was a leader in the Suffrage movement in East Tennessee.
